---
alwaysApply: true
---

All data passed between pipeline stages must use Pydantic models
defined in backend/models/.

All functions must have type hints on parameters and return values.

All LLM API calls must implement retry logic: 3 attempts,
exponential backoff starting at 2 seconds.

File processing functions must handle missing files, corrupt files,
and unsupported formats gracefully with descriptive error messages.